[1m## Installation[0m

[4m### Build from source[0m

[4m#### Prerequisites[0m

[33m-[0m gcc/clang (C++14-compatible)
[33m-[0m libpcre2
[33m-[0m sqlite ≥ 3.9.0
[33m-[0m zlib, bz2
[33m-[0m libcurl ≥ 7.23.0
[33m-[0m libarchive
[33m-[0m libunistring
[33m-[0m wireshark ([35m`tshark`[0m, for pcap support)
[33m-[0m cargo/rust (for PRQL compiler)

[4m#### Build[0m

[35m```console[0m
[35m$ ./autogen.sh    # only needed when building from a git clone[0m
[35m$ ./configure[0m
[35m$ make[0m
[35m$ sudo make install[0m
[35m```[0m

[1m## Usage[0m

[35m```console[0m
[35m$ lnav /path/to/file1 /path/to/dir ...[0m
[35m$ lnav --ioc /path/to/ioc.txt /var/log/auth.log[0m
[35m```[0m

See the [34m[[0mupstream documentation[34m]([0mhttps://docs.lnav.org[34m)[0m for full usage details.

[4m### Usage with [0m[4m[35m`systemd-journald`[0m

[35m```console[0m
[35m$ journalctl [0m[35m|[0m[35m lnav[0m
[35m$ journalctl -f [0m[35m|[0m[35m lnav[0m
[35m$ journalctl -o short-iso [0m[35m|[0m[35m lnav   # include year in timestamps[0m
[35m$ journalctl -o json [0m[35m|[0m[35m lnav        # structured fields (PRIORITY, _SYSTEMD_UNIT, etc.)[0m
[35m```[0m

